{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"761f69a3-bb1b-4bef-bb28-1c608f3f8497","content":"Yes, you'll hit **framework compatibility issues**. Your project targets:\n\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — ❌ Not supported by MSTest v3\n- **`net5.0`** — ❌ Not supported by MSTest v3\n- **`net462`** — ✅ Supported\n\nMSTest v3 dropped support for EOL .NET runtimes. It requires **.NET 6.0+** for .NET Core targets (while .NET Framework 4.6.2+ remains supported).\n\n**To migrate, you'd need to:**\n1. Update `netcoreapp3.1` → `net6.0` (or later)\n2. Update `net5.0` → `net6.0` (or later)\n3. Replace the two package references (`MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter`) with the single consolidated **`MSTest`** package\n\nAlso be aware of behavioral/API breaking changes in v3 (e.g., stricter test lifecycle, some removed APIs). Review the [MSTest v3 migration guide](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/core/testing/mstest-sdk-overview) before upgrading.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b0f9687a-285b-4171-8ed2-b914768ebc0c","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a project that multi-targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. They want to migrate from MSTest v2 (2.2.10) to MSTest v3.\n\nMSTest v3 has some important compatibility changes:\n\n1. **Dropped TFM support**: MSTest v3 dropped support for several older frameworks. Specifically:\n   - `netcoreapp3.1` is **not supported** in MSTest v3 (it was EOL'd)\n   - `net5.0` is **not supported** in MSTest v3 (it was EOL'd)\n   - `net462` should work fine since MSTest v3 supports .NET Framework 4.6.2 and later\n\n2. **Package consolidation**: MSTest v3 consolidates the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages into a single `MSTest` meta-package, though the individual packages are still available.\n\n3. **Breaking changes**: There are various API-level breaking changes in MSTest v3. The core issue is that two of the three target frameworks aren't supported, so I'd need to either drop those targets or stick with MSTest v2.","outputTokens":660,"requestId":"1BD0:A2B8A:AD3E9A:C382D8:6A03ED3E"},"id":"18ca3391-2fbb-4935-8b51-7c114c78d13b","timestamp":"2026-05-13T03:17:31.406Z","parentId":"047760f2-ebcc-4739-8e57-62453d4ecb6d"}
